00:22:28.050 --> 00:22:29.280 align:middle line:90%
>> Yep.

00:22:29.280 --> 00:22:30.530 align:middle line:90%
I think they're very parallel.

00:22:30.530 --> 00:22:32.030 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's
